31
00:02:33,780 --> 00:02:36,074
<i>Yeah... I figured it'd be that...</i>

32
00:02:36,699 --> 00:02:38,117
Well...to be honest,

33
00:02:38,201 --> 00:02:42,705
things have gotten complicated
so I don't know where it is now...

34
00:02:42,914 --> 00:02:44,666
That's so irresponsible.

35
00:02:48,878 --> 00:02:50,672
You're still following me?

36
00:02:51,214 --> 00:02:52,799
Give me back my notebook!

37
00:02:52,882 --> 00:02:54,300
I don't know where it is...

38
