If you want it back, go look for it...

39
00:03:03,601 --> 00:03:06,354
Wammy's House wasn't
simply an orphanage...

40
00:03:07,313 --> 00:03:09,482
it was an institution for
brilliant children...

41
00:03:09,565 --> 00:03:14,904
to raise them to become
the Second L... L's successor...

42
00:03:16,155 --> 00:03:17,699
<i>'1 is successors...</i> ”

43
00:03:17,949 --> 00:03:21,869
The one who ranked at the top
was a boy called Near.

44
00:03:22,412 --> 00:03:24,122
<i>Near... N... Huh?</i>

45
00:03:24,622 --> 00:03:30,586
And the boy N mentioned, Mello,
was ranked next after Near.

46
00:03:31,504 --> 00:03:35,341
<i>Near is L's successor...
There's no mistake...</i>

47
00:03:35,925 --> 00:03:37,885
<i>N is commanding the SPK...</i>

48
00:03:38,469 --> 00:03:42,390
<i>No... Mello probably wanted to
become L's successor...</i>

49
00:03:43,182 --> 00:03:44,767
<i>If that's the case,
Mello would probably</i>

50
00:03:44,851 --> 00:03:48,104
<i>want to use any means necessary
to get the notebook before Near...</i>

51
00:03:48,938 --> 00:03:50,398
<i>Near is convinced
that Mello is involved.</i>

52
00:03:51,065 --> 00:03:54,110
<i>He's certain that he is...</i>

53
00:03:54,986 --> 00:03:56,362
These are sketches
of both of them.

54
00:03:57,488 --> 00:03:58,906
There are no photographs of them.

55
00:04:00,742 --> 00:04:02,493
<i>L's successor...</i>

56
00:04:03,327 --> 00:04:04,537
<i>I'm still...</i>

57
00:04:04,829 --> 00:04:06,330
<i>fighting L...</i>

58
00:04:09,876 --> 00:04:11,169
<i>At any rate,
I have to figure out</i>

59
00:04:11,252 --> 00:04:13,880
<i>where Mello and
his Mafia associates are located...</i>

60
00:04:14,714 --> 00:04:18,092
<i>I've already had Misa check
a list of wanted Mafia members</i>

61
00:04:18,176 --> 00:04:19,635
<i>with her Shinigami eyes...</i>

62
00:04:20,678 --> 00:04:23,514
Oh! There he is! Someone
whose name I can't see!

63
00:04:23,973 --> 00:04:27,560
Number 105! His name is listed
as Jack Neylon, but...

64
00:04:27,810 --> 00:04:29,854
His real name is Kal Snyder!

65
00:04:30,438 --> 00:04:31,939
<i>With the Death Note,</i>

66
00:04:32,023 --> 00:04:35,777
<i>I made Snyder send a letter to
tell me where his hideout is...</i>

67
00:04:36,736 --> 00:04:38,279
<i>It should be coming soon!</i>

68
00:04:41,157 --> 00:04:43,576
Light! You've got a letter...

69
00:04:45,745 --> 00:04:47,038
<i>He's in Los Angeles!</i>

70
00:04:47,705 --> 00:04:50,666
<i>I did it! I've completely
surpassed both of them!</i>

71
00:04:51,876 --> 00:04:55,046
<i>I'm definitely the strongest as long as
I have the Death Note and Misa's eyes!</i>

72
00:05:00,802 --> 00:05:04,555
Light, I've been a big help, haven't I?

73
00:05:05,056 --> 00:05:07,683
Yeah, I love you, Misa.

74
00:05:32,875 --> 00:05:37,505
The only thing I have to do
is see how far I can control people.

75
00:05:38,047 --> 00:05:43,135
<i>I'd like everyone to see me...
so I can talk t0 them.</i>

76
00:05:45,054 --> 00:05:47,181
<i>The owner is Snyder...</i>

77
00:05:47,765 --> 00:05:50,768
<i>I guess I have to make him
touch the notebook...</i>

78
00:05:51,811 --> 00:05:58,192
<i>Oh, well. ..
Wheee. . . plop.</i>

79
00:05:58,526 --> 00:06:01,112
What the hell?
The notebook moved on its own...

80
00:06:03,155 --> 00:06:04,657
It's a notebook that
can kill people.

81
00:06:04,991 --> 00:06:06,742
I wouldn't be surprised
if it were alive!

82
00:06:08,953 --> 00:06:12,373
B-Boss!
The guy with the dirty clothes...

83
00:06:12,748 --> 00:06:13,833
Is he new?

84
00:06:14,250 --> 00:06:16,961
I'm not a new guy,
I'm a Shinigami...

85
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:18,671
Shinigami?

86
00:06:21,048 --> 00:06:23,634
If you want others to see me,

87
00:06:23,718 --> 00:06:26,178
you have to make them
touch the notebook.

88
00:06:28,806 --> 00:06:30,892
He says you can see him
if you touch the notebook...

89
00:06:31,267 --> 00:06:33,185
Everyone, touch it!

90
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:35,104
There's nothing wrong with me!

91
00:06:37,356 --> 00:06:39,692
Fine... Everyone...

92
00:06:40,526 --> 00:06:42,278
Touch the notebook.

93
00:06:43,738 --> 00:06:44,822
- Woah!
- What's this?!

94
00:06:44,906 --> 00:06:46,574
- I couldn't see him before.
- Boss! Shall I kill him?!

95
00:06:52,455 --> 00:06:55,499
It's no use. Humans can't kill me.

96
00:06:58,544 --> 00:07:01,255
Seems this Shinigami's real.

97
00:07:01,339 --> 00:07:03,341
And it looks like
he's telling the truth.

98
00:07:04,926 --> 00:07:09,347
Ryuk. Right now I'm going to
relinquish ownership of this notebook.

99
00:07:09,889 --> 00:07:13,768
Follow the person
who I give it to.

100
00:07:14,435 --> 00:07:16,812
What's this? You're relinquishing
your ownership?

101
00:07:17,188 --> 00:07:20,316
Won't you lose your memory
if you do that?

102
00:07:20,650 --> 00:07:22,151
Misa, lend me your notebook.

103
00:07:23,486 --> 00:07:28,658
If I do this, I won't lose my memory
even if I relinquish my ownership.

104
00:07:29,241 --> 00:07:30,952
I'll give you as many pages
as you need.

105
00:07:31,494 --> 00:07:34,497
From now on, you shall be Kira.
Can you do that?

106
00:07:35,206 --> 00:07:38,876
That's fine, but...
what are you going to do?

107
00:07:39,502 --> 00:07:41,253
I'll explain that right now...

108
00:07:42,380 --> 00:07:43,756
Mistakes will not be allowed.

109
00:07:48,552 --> 00:07:50,471
Chocolate is...good...

110
00:07:50,805 --> 00:07:53,349
Hey! So is what you just said true?!

111
00:07:54,433 --> 00:07:56,310
"If the person using the note
fails to consecutively write

112
00:07:56,394 --> 00:07:58,646
names of people to be killed
within 13 days of each other,

113
00:07:58,729 --> 00:07:59,730
then the user will die."

114
00:08:00,231 --> 00:08:03,317
"if you make this note unusable
by tearing it up or burning it,

115
00:08:03,401 --> 00:08:06,195
all the humans who have touched
the note till then will die."

116
00:08:06,821 --> 00:08:09,573
These two rules were made up?!

117
00:08:10,825 --> 00:08:13,077
Yeah. Those are definitely fake.

118
00:08:13,703 --> 00:08:17,873
A Shinigami probably wrote that
as a joke before giving it to a human.

119
00:08:19,208 --> 00:08:23,504
<i>We can disprove the thirteen-day rule
by using a single person...</i>

120
00:08:24,255 --> 00:08:27,633
<i>The problem is whether this notebook had
passed through Kira's hands or not...</i>

121
00:08:28,134 --> 00:08:31,637
<i>If it has, whether Kira know
these rules were fake or not...</i>

122
00:08:32,763 --> 00:08:36,642
<i>If Kira knows, then they could be
used to his advantage...</i>

123
00:08:37,518 --> 00:08:42,606
<i>Especially the thirteen-day rule which
lets anyone prove they're innocent.</i>

124
00:08:44,859 --> 00:08:47,153
Sidoh, keep guard outside.

125
00:08:48,946 --> 00:08:51,532
You can't be seen by humans, so
at least you're useful for something...

126
00:08:52,241 --> 00:08:53,367
Keep watch outside.

127
00:08:53,701 --> 00:08:54,785
Got it?

128
00:08:55,494 --> 00:08:56,871
<i>What's with this guy?</i>

129
00:08:57,163 --> 00:09:00,291
<i>He's scaly for a human...</i>

130
00:09:06,922 --> 00:09:08,007
This is Yagami.

131
00:09:08,758 --> 00:09:09,759
<i>This is Kira.</i>

132
00:09:10,384 --> 00:09:11,385
What did you say?

133
00:09:11,469 --> 00:09:12,470
Kira?

134
00:09:13,054 --> 00:09:15,848
<i>The notebook that the Japanese
task force had in its possession</i>

135
00:09:15,931 --> 00:09:17,767
<i>was stolen by criminals, wasn't it?</i>

136
00:09:18,392 --> 00:09:21,187
<i>Do you have any proof that
you're Kira?!</i>

137
00:09:21,645 --> 00:09:25,441
<i>Proof? Now that the notebook
has been passed,</i>

138
00:09:25,524 --> 00:09:29,862
<i>there's no way I can prove that
I'm Kira by predicting killings.</i>

139
00:09:30,404 --> 00:09:36,285
<i>But you'll receive proof that
I am Kira soon.</i>

140
00:09:36,911 --> 00:09:38,621
<i>It's my notebook.</i>

141
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,498
What is the meaning of this?

142
00:09:41,082 --> 00:09:44,710
<i>The notebook I'm giving you
allows me to know a person's name</i>

143
00:09:44,794 --> 00:09:47,129
<i>by seeing their face...</i>

144
00:09:48,047 --> 00:09:49,048
<i>Go1' that?</i>

145
00:09:49,256 --> 00:09:50,925
Calm down...

146
00:09:51,342 --> 00:09:53,302
and...listen to...me...

147
00:09:54,303 --> 00:09:57,890
<i>On November 10, at 23:59,</i>

148
00:09:58,724 --> 00:10:02,686
<i>Every mafia member that I have
gathered information on</i>

149
00:10:02,770 --> 00:10:06,315
<i>from the FBI and
other organizations will die.</i>

150
00:10:08,859 --> 00:10:12,530
<i>I've already written it in my notebook,
so it cannot be changed.</i>

151
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:15,991
<i>I also know where their hideout is.</i>

152
00:10:17,034 --> 00:10:18,744
<i>I shall send that information
along with the notebook...</i>

153
00:10:19,411 --> 00:10:20,496
<i>In other words...</i>

154
00:10:20,955 --> 00:10:24,291
<i>On November 10, at 23:59...</i>

155
00:10:25,042 --> 00:10:30,172
<i>This moment is your best chance...
to get the notebook back.</i>

156
00:10:47,982 --> 00:10:49,233
What should we do?

157
00:10:49,650 --> 00:10:52,736
If the members of the mafia are going
to die on the day that Kira specified,

158
00:10:52,820 --> 00:10:54,405
there would be an opportunity.

159
00:10:55,072 --> 00:10:57,992
I resent the idea of following
Kira's plan, but it's a good plan.

160
00:10:58,242 --> 00:10:59,660
That's right.

161
00:11:04,999 --> 00:11:06,000
But it doesn't...

162
00:11:06,375 --> 00:11:09,962
do us any good just by knowing
when the mafia are doing to die.

163
00:11:11,130 --> 00:11:13,507
Mr. lde, you know the answer.

164
00:11:14,133 --> 00:11:16,010
We'll have the Shinigami follow us...

165
00:11:16,385 --> 00:11:20,973
W-We do the eye deal and
kill them for sure...

166
00:11:21,974 --> 00:11:23,517
I'll do the deal.

167
00:11:23,893 --> 00:11:27,354
N-No way! I'll do the deal...

168
00:11:28,063 --> 00:11:31,066
I handed over the notebook
to begin with.

169
00:11:31,775 --> 00:11:35,696
Because of that,
I even thought of killing myself...

170
00:11:36,614 --> 00:11:39,158
I'll use the notebook
to kill the criminals...

171
00:11:40,201 --> 00:11:43,829
And after thirteen days,
I'll die too...

172
00:11:44,997 --> 00:11:48,042
<i>If Dad ever writes a name
in the notebook...</i>

173
00:11:48,792 --> 00:11:49,960
<i>When that happens...</i>

174
00:11:53,005 --> 00:11:56,926
NOVEMBER 10, 23:47

175
00:12:00,846 --> 00:12:03,265
ls everyone ready?

176
00:12:03,766 --> 00:12:04,767
<i>We're ready.</i>

177
00:12:05,226 --> 00:12:07,478
Then... Deputy Director Yagami...

178
00:12:08,646 --> 00:12:11,565
It's time to make the eye deal
with the Shinigami...

179
00:12:15,110 --> 00:12:16,737
Ryuk, please.

180
00:12:17,905 --> 00:12:19,156
I understand...

181
00:12:30,668 --> 00:12:32,127
Deputy Director Yagami,

182
00:12:32,211 --> 00:12:34,672
take a look at the photographs
of the criminals I gave you.

183
00:12:34,922 --> 00:12:36,757
<i>Can you see their names
and lifespans?</i>

184
00:12:37,758 --> 00:12:39,301
Yeah...l can...

185
00:12:40,344 --> 00:12:42,721
Your signal to go is when
their names disappear.

186
00:13:06,203 --> 00:13:07,288
We're going in!

187
00:13:21,135 --> 00:13:23,012
<i>I knew it, Kira was involved...</i>

188
00:13:24,555 --> 00:13:25,681
<i>I never thought he'd go this far...</i>

189
00:13:26,015 --> 00:13:27,766
<i>My perfect plan isn't ready...</i>

190
00:13:28,642 --> 00:13:30,728
<i>Damn! What is Sidoh doing?</i>

191
00:13:32,146 --> 00:13:34,315
Just be quiet and watch, Sidoh!

192
00:13:34,732 --> 00:13:38,485
You'll get your notebook
as long as you don't interfere.

193
00:13:43,324 --> 00:13:44,450
Roy! Skyer!

194
00:13:45,326 --> 00:13:46,577
The notebook is under Rod!

195
00:13:47,077 --> 00:13:48,704
Bring it up to the monitor room!

196
00:13:59,882 --> 00:14:00,883
Don't move!

197
00:14:09,016 --> 00:14:11,393
L, we've captured two of them.

198
00:14:11,602 --> 00:14:12,978
We've also safely retrieved
the notebook!

199
00:14:14,229 --> 00:14:15,356
<i>We're going back now!</i>

200
00:14:16,190 --> 00:14:17,983
No, not yet.

201
00:14:20,277 --> 00:14:22,571
<i>We still haven't found anyone
who resembles Mello.</i>

202
00:14:22,988 --> 00:14:26,116
<i>He's hiding somewhere
in the building.</i>

203
00:14:26,992 --> 00:14:30,537
We've come this far. Use caution,
and hunt him down.

204
00:14:46,678 --> 00:14:48,430
- What's was that?
- An explosion?

205
00:14:50,057 --> 00:14:51,100
Don't move.

206
00:14:51,725 --> 00:14:54,228
I've just blown up
the two entrances.

207
00:14:55,312 --> 00:14:56,605
But that was only a warning.

208
00:14:57,022 --> 00:14:59,316
Next, I'll blow up
the entire building...

209
00:15:01,151 --> 00:15:02,569
<i>Do what I say...</i>

210
00:15:03,570 --> 00:15:04,571
<i>It's Mel/o!</i>

211
00:15:10,661 --> 00:15:14,456
Yagami again, huh?
Maybe I should have killed you?

212
00:15:15,082 --> 00:15:19,920
I never thought I would be bargaining
for the notebook with you again.

213
00:15:24,466 --> 00:15:30,139
M-I-H-A-E-L - K-E-E-H-L...

214
00:15:31,432 --> 00:15:34,309
Your real name is...Mihael Keehl.

215
00:15:34,977 --> 00:15:36,603
<i>Damn it! How did he-?</i>

216
00:15:37,438 --> 00:15:38,564
<i>I did it!</i>

217
00:15:39,314 --> 00:15:41,024
Give up, Mello.

218
00:15:41,650 --> 00:15:44,695
I won't kill you if you surrender.

219
00:15:45,070 --> 00:15:47,448
<i>What? Why are you being stupid?</i>

220
00:15:47,823 --> 00:15:49,575
<i>Hurry! Write his name
in the notebook and kill him!</i>

221
00:15:51,493 --> 00:15:54,788
You'll die if I write your name
in this notebook.

222
00:15:55,456 --> 00:15:58,250
Throw down the detonator
and raise your hands!

223
00:16:06,884 --> 00:16:08,343
- Yagami. ..
- Don't move!

224
00:16:09,011 --> 00:16:10,804
I only have to write your last name!

225
00:16:11,180 --> 00:16:12,347
It won't take a second.

226
00:16:13,098 --> 00:16:15,559
<i>You idiot... Just write it. Write it!</i>

227
00:16:16,351 --> 00:16:20,939
Sorry... I really didn't
want to kill you...

228
00:16:27,196 --> 00:16:29,072
Yagami, you've...

229
00:16:29,865 --> 00:16:31,825
never killed anyone before,
have you?

230
00:16:38,165 --> 00:16:39,166
Gun shots?!

231
00:16:47,174 --> 00:16:48,175
Deputy Director!

232
00:16:48,926 --> 00:16:50,052
Jose! Grab the notebook!

233
00:16:50,844 --> 00:16:52,262
